                    <h3 class="h6 fw-semibold mb-1">Mr. David Okoye</h3>
                    <p class="small text-primary mb-2">Cloud Engineering</p>
                    <p class="small text-muted mb-0">Certified multi-cloud architect supporting DevOps and capstone deploys.</p>
